## Data Compatibility

### Observable Types Conversion

Convert NiceGUI Observable types before passing to grid:

```python
# WRONG - may crash with reactive data
grid = ui.aggrid({"rowData": state.items})

# CORRECT - convert to plain dicts
row_data = [dict(item) for item in state.items]
grid = ui.aggrid({"rowData": row_data})
```

### Handling None Values

```python
def prepare_row_data(items: list[dict]) -> list[dict]:
    rows = []
    for item in items:
        project = item.get("project") or {}
        rows.append({
            "id": item.get("id"),
            "name": item.get("name", ""),
            "project_name": project.get("name") or f"Project {item.get('project_id', 'N/A')}",
        })
    return rows
```

