## Testing Requirements

All grids MUST be tested for:

- [ ] Light mode appearance
- [ ] Dark mode appearance (toggle via UI or browser preference)
- [ ] Dynamic dark/light mode switching without refresh
- [ ] Column filtering works
- [ ] Column sorting works
- [ ] Quick search/filter works
- [ ] Export to CSV works (verify file content)
- [ ] Selection behavior (if applicable)
- [ ] Inline editing (if applicable)
- [ ] Custom cell styling visible in both modes

